{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then the next step after Herta's, I had to do something else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my uncle, Arno Sommerfeld, knew some-- somebody out in the-- in one of the other suburbs of Berlin who ran an insurance business and who was a member of the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't what recall all the details-- and who could use, use somebody as an office clerk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, everybody had to work, you had to register with the-- with the employment department.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody, nobody, from a certain age-- I was then, I'm trying to think, 1943, 16 years old, you know-- then I-- you had to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he took me in as an officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just a-- just as a-- it was a farce.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, it was just a, a pretend job because I was really not at work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It turned out-- I, I think that the man knew-- he knew, of course, who I was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wanted to already buy some insurance for the-- for the-- expecting the time when Germany lost the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so he can say, well, I helped somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that makes me a good guy, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, I mean, really, seriously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A lot of people tried to build this-- build this kind of insurance for themselves that were Nazi party and had the foresight to see that Germany is going to lose the war, and that they're all going to be held accountable for what has--",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--what has gone on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was just-- no, that was just before that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's still--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was '43.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, but actually, I have to go back for a  moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father really died in-- a normal death because of his asthma.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
